{"type": "article", "id": 16100, "title": "TIES 灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-15T06:20:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061531475nIfVhK3FtW1Aq4s.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款像灯笼一样的灯是可拆的，分为吊在天花板下或放在桌上两种，来自荷兰  CRE8 social venture 里年轻的设计师。每一块都是胶合板做的，它们形状一样，可以像积木一样搭建起来，任意改变以适应空间大小。光线通过方块的缝隙里透出，有古典园林的神秘感。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/ceiling-lamp-ties/\" target=\"_blank\"> 这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614345697a8mzBfJsnkUTP0.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143457YHP4UwmXbCpQ2q58.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143458H1QoDYLl4PynbhwI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}